Diablo Mountains, Downtown Walnut Creek and our beautifully landscaped courtyard.', ' Add to that our Hot Tub, and Swimming Pool and Park Place Apartments truly becomes a place fit for a year or lifetime of  enjoyment.', 'Currently Available:', '665 Square Feet', 'Top Floor, same building as laundry room', 'All Electric Kitchen with', 'Microwave', 'Dishwasher', 'Electric Stove', 'Refrigerator', 'Nice Bedroom with large closet', 'Living and Dining Space', '1 parking space in our underground parking garage', '$2245 per month', '$200 holding deposit', 'Find us online at:', '<URL>', 'Park Place Apartments', '1310 Alma Avenue', 'Downtown Walnut Creek', 'show contact info']
